WEBVTT

00:00:08.050 --> 00:00:13.050
Good news is needed now more than ever.

00:00:13.050 --> 00:00:20.469
The good news we need is not of human origin.

00:00:20.469 --> 00:00:25.469
It originates with the giver of real hope, Jehovah God.

00:00:25.469 --> 00:00:29.469
And it centers on His Son, Jesus Christ.

00:00:29.469 --> 00:00:35.929
What is this good news?

00:00:35.929 --> 00:00:37.929
Can we trust it?

00:00:37.929 --> 00:00:40.929
And can it help people right now?

00:00:40.929 --> 00:00:48.810
This year's declared the Good News Convention of Jehovah's Witnesses

00:00:48.810 --> 00:00:53.810
will bolster confidence in God and His Son.

00:00:53.810 --> 00:00:57.810
The good news of God's Kingdom will help you to cope with life now

00:00:57.810 --> 00:01:02.810
and prepare you for eternal life in the future.

00:01:02.810 --> 00:01:06.810
Now that is Good News.
